  "name": "Channel Resistance (2 EP)",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/skills/blue_18.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>An eidolon becomes less easily affected by the channel energy ability of clerics or paladins. The eidolon gains a +2 bonus on any saves that are made to resist the effects of channel energy, including effects that rely on the use of channel energy (such as the Command Undead feat).</p>\n<p>At 7th level, this bonus can be increased to +4 by spending 2 additional evolution points.</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>The eidolon must possess the undead appearance evolution to take this evolution.</p>",
